  <h2 class="slide-h">Built by someone who<br><strong>lives inside the industry.</strong></h2>
  <p class="slide-sub">The founder's credibility is the first unfair advantage. Andrew's presence spans the red carpet and the jobsite — and that cultural range is the brand.</p>
  <div class="founder-wrap">
